OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FRain spreading east this
OL,6,Fmorning, followed by drier, brighter
OL,7,Fconditions. Becoming largely cloudy
OL,8,Fthis afternoon with widespread strong
OL,9,Fwinds and a risk of coastal gales.
OL,10,FScattered showers developing, these
OL,11,Flocally heavy and merging to longer
OL,12,Fperiods of rain in places.
OL,13,
OL,14,CTonight:FRain and showers slowly
OL,15,Ffading away this evening with clearing
OL,16,Fskies overnight. Strong winds also
OL,17,Feasing but a further risk of coastal
OL,18,Fgales across Kent and Sussex at first.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
