OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CSunday:FVariable amounts of could but
OL,6,Fa widely dry, bright and warm day.
OL,7,FRather breezy during the afternoon,
OL,8,Falthough the winds not as strong
OL,9,Fcompared to Saturday.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FCloud
OL,12,Fand rain giving way to sunshine and
OL,13,Fshowers on Monday. Temperatures
OL,14,Ftrending lower. Rather cool and breezy
OL,15,FTuesday and Wednesday with sunny
OL,16,Fspells, scattered showers and possible
OL,17,Fafternoon thunderstorms.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
